# Todo API — Windsurf Rules

Backend Nest.js untuk aplikasi Todo.

## Konvensi
- Modul mengenkapsulasi fitur (todos/, users/)
- Semua endpoint memiliki validasi class-validator
- Response format mengikuti MCP server `todo-shared-context` (`architecture/api-contracts.md`)
- Error handling: 400 (validation), 404 (not found), 422 (business rule), 500 (internal)

## Referensi
- Domain knowledge: MCP server `todo-shared-context` (GitHub: `satryawiguna/todo-shared-ai-native`)
- API contracts: `architecture/api-contracts.md`
- Business rules: `business/business-rules.md`
